Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I did what I could, but this is UTB, so this still Needs a Second Pass}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The love story of two police detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Detective Boys plays a part, {Used Detective Boys instead of Youth Detective Squad}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the case takes a surprising turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees through the one and only truth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the Body of a kid and the mind of an adult,{Originally: No case is left unsolved with Detective Conan.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Officer Sato?!...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it you want to talk to me about?...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What do I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, ha
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:15.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just get inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:17.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What it is?...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What in the world is it?...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I did something wrong again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sato's birthday is in April...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I kept her company at karaoke too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's going to ask me to break up with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:35.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I got you! You fell for it\NAh, ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just great, isn't it?!\NOfficer Takagi, this toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to try it on Yumi next!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Officer Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me you brought me all the way just to try that on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, anything wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're finished work and ready to go home anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:25.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or are you saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't ask you to come with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,unless I have something important to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police Sergeant Takagi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They sure are in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... they're not there yet... {et what?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:42.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're probably going to make it soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Not for some time yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it, will you!,\NOfficer Sato... Aha, ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:55.54,Title,,0,0,0,,Love Story at Police Headquarters 6\N(Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Request for dispatch from the Tottori Prefectural Police...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You do know of them, don't you, Megure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The band of thieves that raided that area,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and are now stealing nation wide...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay... see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:17.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A joint investigation headquarters was set up in Tottori, and they're asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for people from the 1st division investigation section here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Sergeant! Isn't the stealing supposed to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,taken care of by the 3rd division...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've a so committed attempted murder in Tokyo too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, they're sending one person from the 3rd division.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They also need a 1st division-er. Who do we send?... {Def. Need Re-wording}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:39.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:42.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who's single, brilliant, and has high stamina, {Are we sure this isn't a code"Someone who's sing e., brilliant and has robust health enough"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Able to work in a different prefecture...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that person is familiar with the area, it's even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?! That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't his home town somewhere in Tottori?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? W-Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Him... Takagi! Officer Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think he's a good candidate, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:15.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although his appearance doesn't show it, he's pretty sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I hear he's solved a lot of cases too.{wtf is cases toe? Oh now it makes sense}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay then Sergeant,\NI'll notify him tomorrow morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks... that'll be a great help...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's sad to think that he's going to go far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hide's... really going abroad, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still don't know for sure, do we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, England is the place where soccer originated, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you do like him, don't you want him to play at the original location?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, but!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, as far as I'm concerned.\NI feel that it's good idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to go abroad and get tough, more so, for the World Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The World Cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,World Cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's stopped raining...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:13.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hum?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man was heaving hard and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he seemed to be having a hard time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because he's jogging...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:30.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd better hurry or we'll be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:41.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I heard... That's the story...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you listening or what?\NMiwako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miwako?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I'm barely going to make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:51.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything on my face...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?{Original Sub: Huh...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Good... bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm going to be dispatched to tho joint\NInvestigation headquarters in Tottori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aha, ha...\NM-Maybe you got the wrong person...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid! {I think Idoit fits better.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the only Takagi here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't pretend you don't know! {I like: "Don't act stupid" Better but this works}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to Yumi you should've gotten a call from Inspector Megure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?! C-Come to think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did get a call from the inspector this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was still drowsy, so I didn't really follow what he was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See... It's that phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? W-Well I get to come back after the case is solved anyway so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't understand anything, do you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The headquarters is pursuing the robbers that are committing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the serial robberies nation wide, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In most cases like these, who knows how many incidents there are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And besides, if there are several members involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who knows, when the case"ll be solved...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, things will work out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With his ability
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three years will be to solve the case... {Orginal: will probably be enough}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Three ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three ears.\N1095 days...26280 hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Heavens have not forsaken me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:47.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The air is clean in Totton and you can eat all you want of Matsuba crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can ride camels at the sand dunes of Tottori too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, O-Officer Sate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to send me 20th Century.\NJapanese Pears, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're my favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aha, ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's thee WORD!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsuba Crab is our favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the camels while you're at it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's with all this noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scene of the crime\NIs on the 23rd floor of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The skyscraper located on Beika city 4th District!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man was found stabbed to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to report by investigators,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who found the corpse seems to be a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato and Takagi, go to the scene of the crime Together!{Together was"On the double"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:41.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megure you take care, of giving orders at the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please have Cho-san take care of things this time Sergeant. {Why is this the only time Honorifics was used?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the scene immediately! {Originally: On the double}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the first tame I'm teaming with you, isn't it. Cho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's get to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:02.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is a veteran that's 2 years older than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Learn a lot from him, will you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, this may be the last time he'll be teaming with you.{Originaly"This may be the last time he'll be teaming with you, besides..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aaaaagh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Officer Takagi.\NG-Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, ha...\NAre you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hide's press conference will start at noon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:36.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:38.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd better hurry, or we'll miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hide's press conference will be on the news of today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:44.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll probably be aired several times all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somethings seems to have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The name of the man that was stabbed is\NMr. Hirotoshi Nakamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was 27, an office worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon is\Na knife of 18 centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time of the murder is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Between 07:00 to 07:30 today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, his colleague at work came here at 13:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And found him dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I took a day off from work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And was supposed to go with him to reserve our wedding hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-How could something like this happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know of anyone who may have had a grudge against him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was the type to make enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the killer is an acquaintance of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the door was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:35.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, will you pick out the person...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:39.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think may have had a grudge against him from the album?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go check the person out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you see something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's Officers Takagi and Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So... take care of it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:51.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bet its a homicide case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, didn't it happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around a little after 07:00 this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Officer Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-How do you know?!...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw a suspicious person on our way to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the street near this condo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on. Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man was just jogging and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember!\NJust before we passed that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It stopped raining, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... It was a showers that lasted about 10 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:27.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that guy's clothes, was hardly wet at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was that the case? {Original: Why do you think it wasn't wet?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was taking shelter from the rain somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it started raining while, he was jogging...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he started running again because it stopped raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fool! If had stopped for 10 minutes.\NHe wouldn't be heaving like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, he wasn't out of breath because he was jogging...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But because he was hyper...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from having stabbed someone in a room near here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what you wanted to say, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:01.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, is that man here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-This man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sort of looks like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Mr. Kato, a colleague of his at work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly... I heard that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he was freeloading at his friend's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know where that house is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? A little after 07:00 this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was here right through...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! You're the one who stabbed Hirotoshi aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?\NMe, commit murder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what are you talking about?!\NOut of nowhere...{Originally: the blue like that}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:36.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on!\NCut out the noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you to get rid of door-to-door sales, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well... the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Oh Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:48.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Officer Chiba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh this is interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!\NSuspect of a homicide case?!...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Kato?!...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:01.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His colleague at work,\NMr. Hirotoshi Nakamoto was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon was a knife, that found on the floor beside the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-And the estimated time of death was?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Between 07:00 to 07:30 this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he couldn't have committed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he woke me up at 07:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:27.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we were here together watching TV till 08:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we were watching\NNichiuri TV's live morning broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Morning Live Seven", a news variety program...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:40.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Officer Chiba, he woke you up, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it could be that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he showed you something that he had video taped some time ago, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got proof too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, why, am I suspected in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you're my ex-boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an eye-witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:15:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That says he saw you a little past 07:00 near the condo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that guy wasn't half asleep and mistook me for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We weren't half asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him clearly! It was him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was wearing a gray parka top...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were running with a black knapsack on your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as If you were jogging...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have Officer Chiba show us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And show us proof that he was watching TV with that man
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from 07:00 to 08:00 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What? What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a mess!\NI can see why you're always late for work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm doing the best I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm recently not as tardy as\NI used to be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I sort of did something to give me initiative to get up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with these toys here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, you're some special effects freak or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Who cares!\NI mean after all, it's just a hobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's Gomeral Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamen Yaiba is here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a rare object made of tin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:09.28,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!\NDon't get rough with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you to wait in the car with Mr. Kato and Ms. Shimura, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The evidence you mentioned that both of you were watching TV together...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, sir!\NIt's this video tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Yoko Okino's 4 minute cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's February 25th. Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:35.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I video tape this corner of the Morning Live Seven each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I watched rental videos with Kato while drinking and fell asleep here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot to pre-set the program to record of so I recorded it myself today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he couldn't have shown me something he recorded beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, only one video tape deck is used.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there's another deck here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:58.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's one that we only use sometimes for dubbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he used that deck,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the cord would show in front of the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would notice it no matter how drowsy I may be... {"I may be" seems of in this context "I would have..., ...I was" sounds better.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you think, it's a lie, call the TV station and confirm it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the corner after
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nichiruri TV's Morning Live Seven's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weather forecast of today, February 25, Friday... {He definetly didn't say that but whatever UTB}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, you have many marks\NIn other places too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the cable TV programs are marked...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are so man, programs\NI want to watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. That's why you've got\NSO many memo pads stuck all over-the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And? After watching the program until 08:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I watched videos from 08:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well... that's
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba, hey! Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! It's this, this here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:17:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It, It's Kamen Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is episode 1 of the first Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mask of the first Yiaiba was, really gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that was one of the good points!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, how long were you watching this children's program?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I watched one 120 minute tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean you watched it for 2 hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's taped on 3 times the regular speed and the commercials aren't cut so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:46.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Six hours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, did you video tape all the tapes Officer Chiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kato gave me the ones he taped before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, were you with him right through?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:19:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, after watching half the program\NI went to take a shower,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for about 30 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I started watching again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I watched all the way to episode 12 and stopped the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then professional baseball was being aired so,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, the game from 14:00 the Falcons vs: the Jaguars!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was 2:05 when you, Cho, came while I was watching that game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From here to the victim's condo,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would take at least an hour by car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If after watching TV for an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they watched the video for approximately 6 hours together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His alibi is established...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to be sure,\NLet's look for the gray parka top and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,black knapsack the man had on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!\NIs that for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:58.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:19:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there's nothing, don't shout!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, how long is the dispatch to Tottori going to be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,besides
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guys at the 1st division say\NIt will be about 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what did Officer Sato say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wants me to get her\NSOME Japanese pears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.39,0:20:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange... It's mere natural that she would get more upset...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although, I'll be dispatched it seems I get to take off once a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I can call her frequently too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you don't end up like Kato...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:33.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was abroad on a business trip till last month,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But as soon as he got back he called me and asked me to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While he was away, the woman he was\Nliving with started going with another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he was left without a place to stay, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-And...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used to call her everyday, and yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he complained he could never understand women...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're serious about her,\NI think you should let her know, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About how you feel and what your plans are for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, you never know what'll happen to you either, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may end up finding a lover over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that happens.\NYou won't be coming home for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is said that the hearts of people, proportionately pull apart the more time passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although there are rare exceptions.{Original: Although there rarely seems to be exceptions at times}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, will never go with a woman other than her! Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just who are we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:39.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:41.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were talking about Hide
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he may be going out abroad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hide...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it seems that\NHide decided to remain in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:53.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You saw the press conference they had in the afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.88,0:21:56.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, right after Morning Live Seven started,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:21:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a flash news report subtitle displayed on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It said, "Player Hide Akashire of the Tokyo\NSpirits have: announced that he will remain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A press conference will he held at 12:00 noon"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, did the caster mention anything about that news later?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.77,0:22:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's the story!...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's not possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.78,0:22:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if this trick were to be used, there are still...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some parts I cannot explain.
